videos.headline: Masterful trickery from USC special teams leads to TD
videos.description: The UCLA punt unit is completely fooled as USC collapses to one side, leaving Michael Pittman Jr. wide open on the left side of the field who is able to trot into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Rosen tosses first TD pass of QB duel
videos.description: Josh Rosen moves the UCLA offense 80 yards down the field, ending with this 11-yard touchdown pass to Jordan Lasley.

videos.headline: USC answers with rushing TD
videos.description: The Trojans move the ball quickly downfield and end their drive with a 2-yard touchdown run from Ronald Jones II to take the lead in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Darnold delivers great pass after scrambling
videos.description: Sam Darnold is forced out of the pocket and ends up hitting Tyler Vaughns 15 yards downfield who dives to make the finger-tip grab.

videos.headline: Darnold errant pass gets picked
videos.description: Sam Darnold dances around and sails a pass over the receiver's hands and into the waiting arrms of Jaleel Wadood for an interception.

videos.headline: Rosen gets crushed, USC recovers fumble
videos.description: Josh Rosen has the pocket collapse on him and gets hit by Malik Dorton, forcing the fumble that is recovered by John Houston Jr. to give the Trojans the ball late in the first half

videos.headline: Darnold throws impressive pass to the sideline
videos.description: Sam Darnold looks downfield and throws and a professional-level throw to the sideline to Deontay Burnett who is able to snag the pass and keep his feet in bounds for the first down.

videos.headline: Rosen intercepted in the end zone
videos.description: Josh Rosen forces a pass into traffic end zone and Marvel Tell III is there to pick it off in the end zone and run it back to the USC 23-yard line.

videos.headline: Darnold keeps for a rushing TD
videos.description: Sam Darnold shows off his agility and makes moves to get in to the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Rosen tosses 2nd TD of the night
videos.description: Josh Rosen connects with Jordan Lasley for a touchdown for the second time of the game and the Bruins claw to within seven.

videos.headline: Lasley keeps his eyes on the prize
videos.description: Josh Rosen's pass downfield to Jordan Lasley gets knocked around twice, bouncing off of a USC helmet before Jordan Lasley is able to corral the pass for 43 yards.

videos.headline: Jones II barrels through the line for 2nd TD
videos.description: Ronald Jones II adds his second rushing touchdown of the night on this 2-yard run to make it a two-score game.

videos.headline: Rosen to Lasley for the TD hat-trick
videos.description: Josh Rosen connects with Jordan Lasley for a touchdown for the third time in the game. UCLA down only five after a failed 2-point conversion.

videos.headline: USC coach Helton says team needs a nap
videos.description: USC head coach Clay Helton describes the resiliency of his team and how after playing 12 weeks straight, the Trojans earned some much needed rest.

videos.headline: Darnold: 'Great victory against a great UCLA team'
videos.description: USC QB Sam Darnold looks back on the Trojans' hard-fought victory over the Bruins and looks ahead at the rest week ahead of the Pac-12 Championship.

videos.headline: USC takes down UCLA in a QB showdown
videos.description: Chris Fowler and Kirk Herbstreit break down how the Trojans were able to ride in to victory over the Bruins.

videos.headline: USC withstands UCLA
videos.description: The Trojans use three rushing touchdowns, with Ronald Jones II running for 122 yards and two touchdowns, in a 28-23 win against the Bruins.

videos.headline: USC wins with balanced attack
videos.description: Sam Darnold and USC beat the UCLA Bruins with help from special teams and the run game.
